name: Ingham Health Dept.
tweet: Know your status! ICHD is providing free, confidential, & anonymous HIV testing to MI residents on World AIDS Day on Dec. 1st from 8 am – 3 pm at Forest Community Health Center (2316 S. Cedar St. Lansing).   For more info, call the HIV/STI prevention program at 517-887-4424.  https://t.co/XEYmrekXa2
